OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry start with sunny spells.
OL,6,FScattered showers developing, before
OL,7,Fclearing during the afternoon,
OL,8,Fallowing widespread sunshine later.
OL,9,FTemperatures cooler than yesterday for
OL,10,Fmost, perhaps a little warmer near
OL,11,Fcoasts, but still warm overall.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA dry night with clear
OL,14,Fspells, and overnight temperatures
OL,15,Frather fresher than of late especially
OL,16,Fin rural spots. Light winds.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSaturday:FDry with hazy sunshine and
OL,19,Fvery warm for many again on Saturday.
OL,20,FCloud thickening somewhat overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
