OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FTurning
OL,6,Fmore unsettled and cooler into the
OL,7,Fstart of next week. Temperatures
OL,8,Ffalling nearer normal for the time of
OL,9,Fyear. Becoming breezy with outbreaks
OL,10,Fof occasionally heavy rain or showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
